OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FContent warning: This report contains
OL,8,Fdetails that some readers may find
OL,9,Fupsetting
OL,11,FA woman who claims she was raped as a
OL,12,Fchild by Sir Jeffrey Donaldson has
OL,13,Fsaid she should have brought the
OL,14,Falleged abuse to police years earlier
OL,15,Fbut had "tried not to be a victim".
OL,26,@wD@IOUwD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
