PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FContinuing to give evidence at Newry
OL,8,FCrown Court, the woman also denied she
OL,9,Fhad raised the allegations as a
OL,10,Fteenager as a way of getting out of
OL,11,Fattending a Christian centre in Co
OL,12,FAntrim.
OL,14,FThe woman, known as complainant B, is
OL,15,Fthe older of two alleged victims who
OL,16,Fhave accused the former DUP leader of
OL,17,Fsexual abuse.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe court has previously heard details
OL,8,Fof her claim that she was raped when
OL,9,Fof primary school age by the former
OL,10,Fpolitician.
OL,12,FTen of the 18 sex abuse charges
OL,13,FDonaldson denies relate to complainant
OL,14,FB, with the offences allegedly
OL,15,Fcommitted between 1985 and 1991.
OL,17,FEleanor Donaldson denies several
OL,18,Fcharges of aiding and abetting her
OL,19,Fhusband's alleged offending.
OL,21,FShe is facing a trial of the facts.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
