OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FOn Wednesday morning, barrister for
OL,8,FJeffrey Donaldson, Kieran Vaughan KC,
OL,9,Fresumed his cross-examination of
OL,10,Fcomplainant B at Newry Crown Court.
OL,12,FDonaldson sat in the dock at the back
OL,13,Fof the courtroom.
OL,15,FMr Vaughan said that complainant B had
OL,16,Fbeen sent to the Christian Family
OL,17,FCentre in Armoy after she had started
OL,18,Fto take drugs in her teenage years.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe told the court that she had taken
OL,8,Fecstasy and marijuana, but denied that
OL,9,Fshe was addicted to the substances.
OL,11,FHe said: "That is the background to
OL,12,Fhow you ended up in Armoy."
OL,14,FShe responded: "Yes."
OL,16,FHe said: "You didn't enjoy being taken
OL,17,Fto Armoy at that time?"
OL,19,FShe said: "I didn't know anybody ...
OL,20,Fit was so far away."
OL,26,@sD@JOUtD@[O]vD@POUvD@UO]xD@JOUyD@WO]{D@
OL,26,AKOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FComplainant B added that she
OL,8,Foriginally thought her issues could
OL,9,Fhave been "dealt with at home", but
OL,10,Fsaid going there "turned out probably
OL,11,Fone of the best things that ever
OL,12,Fhappened to me".
OL,14,FThe barrister said while at the
OL,15,Fcentre, complainant B had spoken to a
OL,16,Fwoman at the facility.
OL,18,FThe witness confirmed she had told her
OL,19,Fabout alleged abuse by Donaldson, but
OL,20,Fdid not go into details.
OL,26,@qD@KOUqD@^O]rD@ROUtD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Vaughan said: "Did you tell her it
OL,8,Fwas sexual abuse?"
OL,10,FShe said: "I am pretty sure I did."
OL,12,FWhen asked if she had told her about
OL,13,Fthe alleged rape, the woman said she
OL,14,Fhad never told anybody about that
OL,15,Fbefore she told police.
OL,17,FThe barrister asked: "Was this in some
OL,18,Fway a part of you trying to get out of
OL,19,FArmoy?"
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@RO]rD@KOUrD@cO]yD@VOU{D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FShe responded: "No, I had friends up
OL,8,Fthere ... it wasn't that in any way
OL,9,Fwhatsoever."
OL,11,FAsked if it was an attempt to deflect,
OL,12,Fshe said "definitely not".
OL,14,FThe barrister said she had then spoken
OL,15,Fto a pastor at the centre about the
OL,16,Fallegations.
OL,18,FShe said: "I felt he was a safe person
OL,19,Fto say this to."
OL,26,@oD@POUqD@LO]tD@JOUtD@YO]zD@KOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FMr Vaughan asked why her conversation
OL,8,Fwith the pastor was not in her
OL,9,Fstatement to police.
OL,11,FShe said: "It was just something I
OL,12,Fforgot about ... I should have
OL,13,Fremembered."
OL,15,FThe barrister asked her if she
OL,16,Fremembered the pastor saying he would
OL,17,Fgot to the police.
OL,19,FShe said: "I don't remember that."
OL,26,@sD@KOUuD@LO]{D@KOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,FThe barrister asked her if she had
OL,8,Ftold the pastor not to go to police,
OL,9,Fand that if he did, she would say it
OL,10,Fwas "all a lie".
OL,12,FShe said: "I don't remember that ...
OL,13,Fif I did it would have been the
OL,14,Fstupidest thing I ever said."
OL,16,FComplainant B added: "I should have
OL,17,Fsaid 'please go, I will go with you'."
OL,19,F"I should have, I was so afraid of
OL,20,Fthis, of what this is.
OL,26,@rD@EOUrD@OO]tD@KOUvD@]O]xD@VOUyD@fO]{D@
OL,26,AAOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1780503064
OL,3,CWoman who alleges Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,4,Crape 'tried not to be a victim', court
OL,5,Ctold
OL,7,F"I didn't want it to be made a thing
OL,8,Fof, I was so embarrassed."
OL,10,FShe added: "I tried to move on, to be
OL,11,Fthe bigger person.
OL,13,F"I tried not to be the victim, I tried
OL,14,Fto build a life."
OL,16,FThe court had previously heard
OL,17,Fcomplainant B state that Donaldson had
OL,18,Fmet her at the Christian centre and
OL,19,Fapologised.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@ZO]rD@LOUuD@AOUvD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
